trans-unit.source: Provides the implementation for the server channel sink provider that creates <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSink"></xref> instances.
trans-unit.target: Fornece a implementação para o servidor do fornecedor de receptor de canal que cria <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSink"> </xref> instâncias.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSink> is used to create Web Services Description Language (WSDL) schema in situations where the URL ends with the string "?wsdl", for example, http://localhost/longbeard?wsdl.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSink>é utilizado para criar o esquema do Web Services Description Language (WSDL) em situações em que o URL termina com a cadeia "? wsdl", por exemplo, http://localhost/longbeard?wsdl.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSink>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider"></xref> class with default values.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider"> </xref> classe com valores predefinidos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider"></xref> class with specified properties and provider data.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider"> </xref> classe com propriedades especificadas e dados do fornecedor.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> of configuration properties to use with the new instance of <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>das propriedades de configuração para utilizar com a nova instância do <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider"> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.SinkProviderData"></xref> instances to use with the new instance of <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BinaryServerFormatterSinkProvider"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>de <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.SinkProviderData"> </xref> instâncias para utilizar com a nova instância do <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BinaryServerFormatterSinkProvider"> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The channel for which to create the channel sink chain.
trans-unit.target: O canal para o qual pretende criar a cadeia de receptores de canal.

trans-unit.source: The first sink of the newly formed channel sink chain.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro receptor da cadeia de receptores de canal recentemente formado.

trans-unit.source: Returns the channel data for the channel that the current sink is associated with.
trans-unit.target: Devolve os dados de canal para o canal de que o sink atual se encontra associado.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IChannelDataStore"></xref> object in which the channel data is to be returned.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IChannelDataStore"> </xref> objeto no qual os dados de canal estão a ser devolvido.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the next <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IServerChannelSinkProvider"></xref> in the sink provider chain.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o seguinte <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IServerChannelSinkProvider"> </xref> na cadeia de fornecedor de receptores.

trans-unit.source: The next <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IServerChannelSinkProvider"></xref> in the sink provider chain.
trans-unit.target: A próxima <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IServerChannelSinkProvider"> </xref> na cadeia de fornecedor de receptores.
